<subSubSection pageId="386" pageNumber="387" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="386.[151,1437,1266,1725]" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[267,500,1518,1545]" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" pagination="5 - 37" refId="ref369927" refString="Rondani, C. (1869 a) Ortalidinae italicae collectae, distinctae et in ordinem dispositae. Dipterologiae italicae prodromi. Pars VII. Fasc. 3 Linea A. Ortaloidi. Dipt. Stirps XX. Ortalidinae Rndn. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 1 (1), 5 - 37." type="journal article" year="1869">Rondani (1869a: 30)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName box="[622,802,1519,1545]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Ortalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fastuosa">
<emphasis box="[622,802,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">Ortalis fastuosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without specifying the exact 
<taxonomicName box="[1135,1221,1519,1545]" family="Number" pageId="386" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
of specimens: “ 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">
bis tantum in 
<taxonomicName box="[314,510,1555,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Opomyzidae" genus="Pedemontio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lecta">Pedemontio lecta</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
[collected in 
<collectingRegion box="[666,773,1555,1581]" country="Italy" name="Piemonte" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">Piedmont</collectingRegion>
twice only]”, from material received from G. Genè and L. Bellardi. 
<bibRefCitation author="Soos, A." box="[303,494,1590,1617]" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" pagination="253 - 260" refId="ref373879" refString="Soos, A. (1983) Untersuchungen des Typenmaterials der Rondanischen Sammlung. 2. Otitidae (Diptera). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae, 29 (1 - 3), 253 - 260." type="journal article" year="1983">Soós (1983: 257)</bibRefCitation>
incorrectly designated a male 
<typeStatus box="[833,922,1591,1617]" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">neotype</typeStatus>
in the MZUF (Box 31) labeled: 1621 / 
<taxonomicName authority="Fall." authorityName="Fallen" authorityYear="1810" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Ortalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1357,1436,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">Ortalis</emphasis>
Fall.
</taxonomicName>
/ 
<taxonomicName authority="Rnd., Pedem." authorityName="Rnd., Pedem." box="[272,525,1627,1653]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Ortalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fastuosa">
<emphasis box="[272,365,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="386" pageNumber="387">fastuosa</emphasis>
Rnd., Pedem.
</taxonomicName>
/ Bois Champeaux, 3/6/77. The specimen in the MRSN, which 
<bibRefCitation author="Soos, A." box="[1243,1436,1626,1653]" pageId="386" pageNumber="387" pagination="253 - 260" refId="ref373879" refString="Soos, A. (1983) Untersuchungen des Typenmaterials der Rondanischen Sammlung. 2. Otitidae (Diptera). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae, 29 (1 - 3), 253 - 260." type="journal article" year="1983">Soós (1983: 258)</bibRefCitation>
also mentioned, actually belongs to Rondani’s original type series and its presence thus invalidates Soós’s 
<typeStatus pageId="386" pageNumber="387">neotype</typeStatus>
(I.C.Z.N. 1999: Article 75.8).
</paragraph>
